-- Berlusconi Party Chief Says No Second Term for Monti: Giornale
-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 2012-11-12T07:40:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-12/berlusconi-party-chief-says-no-second-term-for-monti-giornale.html
Angelino Alfano, general secretary
of Silvio Berlusconi’s People of Liberty party, won’t renew an
alliance with a center-left party that would allow Monti to
return to power after elections, Giornale says, citing Alfano’s
comments on TV program “In Mezz’ora.”
*Alfano says party may change its name and symbol: Giornale
*NOTE: Italians to vote by April in national elections for new
government.  Editor:  Andrew Davis   To contact the reporter on this story:
